{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1339f8cc10","title":"湖南的农民","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"28ef9b93f8","index":0,"year":1926,"month":11,"day":30,"articleId":"1339f8cc10"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji3","name":"毛泽东全集第3卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji3.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4583f276e4","type":"paragraph","text":"湖南的农民（1926年11月30日）","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"1339f8cc10"},{"id":"3a9f543a05","type":"paragraph","text":"现时已有组织的农民一、县农民协会的统计正式成立县农民协会者：三十六县已有县农民协会筹备处者：一十八县共计五十四县二、人数的统计（一）自本月统计的，三十县，五十三万六千一百三十七人按上月统计算的，十一县，五万零五千人无统计估算的，十三县，三万人共计五十四县，计一百零七方一千一百三十七人（二）有十万人以上的-四县有五万人以上的——六县有一万人以上的——十二县有五千人以上的——十二县有一千人以上的一—十八县不满一千人的——二县（三）人数最多的县份有十四万人人数最少的县份有二百七十四人（四）各县人数统计表说明：A为本月有详细报告的：B.按上月报告推算的：C无统计估算的：D.县协筹备处。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"1339f8cc10"},{"id":"1c4d6c6770","type":"paragraph","text":"一万一千二百南县","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"1339f8cc10"},{"id":"9393186cff","type":"paragraph","text":"七干","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"1339f8cc10"},{"id":"755fa1a167","type":"paragraph","text":"茶陵","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"1339f8cc10"},{"id":"1eb0fd1e88","type":"paragraph","text":"A","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"1339f8cc10"},{"id":"b8573ac016","type":"paragraph","text":"六十六八万八千","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"1339f8cc10"},{"id":"d2122e48b7","type":"paragraph","text":"一千四百衡阳","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"1339f8cc10"},{"id":"3e60b1f1b0","type":"paragraph","text":"道县","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":